---
// Full-bleed video hero — Fondation-Tunisie style.
// Header sits over the hero; reduced-motion users see the static poster.
---

<section class="relative w-full h-[100svh] min-h-[640px] overflow-hidden bg-bg">
  <!-- Video layer -->
  <video
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover motion-reduce:hidden"
    poster="/video/hero-poster.jpg"
    autoplay
    muted
    loop
    playsinline
    preload="metadata"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <source src="/video/hero.webm" type="video/webm" />
    <source src="/video/hero.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
  </video>
  <img
    src="/video/hero-poster.jpg"
    alt=""
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover hidden motion-reduce:block"
    aria-hidden="true"
  />

  <!-- Overlays: vertical gradient for legibility + ambient solar wash -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(7,9,13,0.55)_0%,rgba(7,9,13,0.25)_30%,rgba(7,9,13,0.45)_60%,rgba(7,9,13,0.92)_100%)]"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(800px_400px_at_85%_30%,rgba(245,176,65,0.18),transparent_60%)] mix-blend-screen"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- Subtle grid texture, faded -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 grid-bg opacity-[0.06] pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative h-full container-wide flex flex-col justify-end pb-20 lg:pb-28 pt-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow text-ink-soft reveal">
        Cleanoov · Innovation solaire tunisienne
      </p>

      <h1 class="mt-6 text-ink reveal" style="text-wrap: balance;">
        L'énergie du soleil,<br />
        <span class="gradient-solar italic font-semibold">décuplée</span> par la technique.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 text-lg lg:text-xl text-ink-soft max-w-2xl leading-relaxed reveal">
        Nous concevons des solutions de nettoyage et d'installation photovoltaïque
        qui restaurent jusqu'à <span class="text-ink font-medium">25 %</span> du rendement
        d'une centrale solaire — sur le terrain, en Tunisie.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-9 flex flex-wrap gap-4 reveal">
        <a href="/#innovation" class="btn btn-primary">
          Notre démarche
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 7h8M7 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/#realisations" class="btn btn-secondary">
          Voir nos chantiers
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Award strip -->
      <div class="mt-12 lg:mt-16 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 reveal">
        <span class="chip chip-solar">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M6 1l1.5 3 3.5.5-2.5 2.5.5 3.5-3-1.7-3 1.7.5-3.5L1 4.5 4.5 4 6 1z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
          Lauréat iptic
        </span>
        <span class="chip chip-solar">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M6 1l1.5 3 3.5.5-2.5 2.5.5 3.5-3-1.7-3 1.7.5-3.5L1 4.5 4.5 4 6 1z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
          Lauréat ctama · 100 K TND
        </span>
        <span class="chip chip-leaf">
          <span class="dot-pulse" style="width:6px;height:6px"></span>
          Exposants — JCI World Congress
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll indicator -->
    <a
      href="#mission"
      class="absolute bottom-8 right-6 lg:right-12 hidden md:flex items-center gap-3 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ink-muted hover:text-ink transition-colors"
      aria-label="Faire défiler"
    >
      <span>Scroll</span>
      <span class="block w-px h-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-ink-muted to-transparent"></span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
